            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
    <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De ratione morali consideratione</head>
    <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>
      ¶ De ratione morali considerantione. Rubrica 4
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/><ref>Plato in menone:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e123">Quotiens
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>absque mente audet homo
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>leditur: quotiens vero cum mente pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>ficitur.</quote> 
               <!--149.xml-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e135">
               <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>
             ¶ <ref>Aristoteles ethicorum lib. i. ca. 8. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e141">Omnia
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>consonant rationi.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e147">
               <ref>Idem magnorum moralium
        <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>li. 2 c. 3</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e149">Que fiunt absque ratione iudicante
        <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>directiones a fortuna sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e152"> /
               <ref>Idem physicorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>li. 8. c. 3</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e154">Ordinatio omnis ratio est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e160">
               <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>
             ¶ <ref>Tullius tusculanarum questionum libro. 3</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e164" source="http://scta.info/resource/ctd99a-cuh77a-d1e164@95-112">Munus animi est ratione bene vti. Sa
        <lb ed="#V" n="53" break="no"/>pientis animus ita semper affectus est vt ra
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>tione optime vtatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e174"> /
               <ref>Lib. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e176">Bene adhi
        <lb ed="#V" n="55" break="no"/>bita ratio cernit quid optimum sit neglecta vero
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>multis implicatur erroribus. Nihil sine ra
        <lb ed="#V" n="57" break="no"/>tione recte fieri potest</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e186"> /
               <ref>Idem de legibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e188">Quid est non dicam in homine: sed in omni
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>caelo atquem terra ratione diuinius: que cum ado
        <lb ed="#V" n="60" break="no"/>leuit perfecta est nominatur rite sapientia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
               <ref>Li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e202">Lex vera atque princeps apta ad iu
        <lb ed="#V" n="62" break="no"/>bendum et ad vetandum ratio est recta.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e208"> /
               <ref>Idem
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>de fine bonorum et malorum li. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e210">Rationis
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>perfectio est virtus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e216">
               <ref>Idem de natura deo
        <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>rum li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e218">Nihil est mente et ratione melius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e221">
               <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>
             ¶ <ref>Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum li. 5. e. 8</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e225">Si
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>vis omnia tibi subiicere: subiice te rationi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e231">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
               <ref>Li. 8. e. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e235">Ratio nihil aliud est quam incorpus
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>humanum pars diuini spiritus mersa. Nul
        <lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>lum bonum fine ratione est. Quicquid ve
        <lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>ra ratio commendat solidum et eternum est: firmat
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>animum: attollitque futurum semper in excelso.
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>Uirtus non aliud quam recta ratio est: omnes vir
        <lb ed="#V" n="74" break="no"/>tutes rationes sunt. Sequitur ratio naturam
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>quid ergo est ratio: nature imitatio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e254"> /
               <ref>18 ti. e. 2</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e256">Ratione valentius nihil est: casum dolorem
        <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>que et iniuriam subigit. Ama rationem: huius
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>te amor contra durissima armabit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e266"> /
               <ref>17
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>ti. e 4. et pe.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e268">Omnia ad rationem reuocanda sunt</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e274">
               <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>
               <ref>Idem de beneficiis li. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e278">Nihil sine ratio
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>ne faciendum est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e284">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
             ¶ <ref>Lex diges. ti. de legibus. l. infrascripta.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e288">Non
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>omnium que a maioribus constituta sunt ra
        <lb ed="#V" n="84" break="no"/>tio reddi potest.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e297"> /
               <ref>Ti. ad le. acquilis. l. ita vul
        <lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>neratus:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e299">Multa iure ciuili contra rationem dispu
        <lb ed="#V" n="86" break="no"/>tandi pro vtilitate communi recepta sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e307">
               <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>
             ¶ <ref>Maximianus:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e311">Plus ratio quamuis ceca va
        <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>lere solet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-d1e317">
               <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>
             ¶ <ref>Cassiodorus epistolarum li. i. e. 9</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d46602-Qd1e321">Fidem siqui
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>dem rerum a ratione colligimus: que nunquam <!--150.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="62-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>desiderantibus absconditur si suis vestigiis
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>perquiratur.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
